Fuck.

01:50.666 --> 01:52.125
My name is Doyle.

01:53.625 --> 01:55.375
Lord Doyle.

02:00.041 --> 02:02.208
I'm a high roller on a slippery slope.

02:04.958 --> 02:07.375
A gambler with a pair of lucky gloves.

02:10.416 --> 02:12.666
Washed up on the shores of Macau.

02:14.958 --> 02:17.083
The gambling capital of the universe.

02:18.833 --> 02:20.458
City of miracles

02:21.416 --> 02:23.500
in a land saved from the sea.

02:29.083 --> 02:30.750
But I no longer believe in miracles.

02:32.666 --> 02:36.583
And in a few days,
my life as I know it will be over.

02:58.583 --> 02:59.666
Bollocks.

04:48.916 --> 04:50.125
Reception center.

04:56.750 --> 04:59.000
Not playing house tonight, Lord Doyle?

05:00.125 --> 05:03.375
Not tonight, Kai.
No, I practically bled this place dry.

05:03.875 --> 05:07.291
If I win any more money from the Royale,
they'll be paying you in arrears.

05:07.791 --> 05:09.166
Order me a car, would you?

05:09.250 --> 05:11.166
My sincere apologies, Lord Doyle,

05:11.250 --> 05:13.958
but I'm told the hotel limousines
are all tied up tonight.

05:15.041 --> 05:16.041
All of them?

05:16.708 --> 05:18.250
Shall I call you a taxi?

05:18.750 --> 05:20.625
Never mind. It's a pleasant evening.

05:20.708 --> 05:22.000
I think I'll walk.

05:23.958 --> 05:24.958
Do you mind?

05:31.458 --> 05:35.541
All I need is one big win, Kai,
and they'll be throwing limousines at me.

05:37.416 --> 05:39.166
Try the Rainbow Casino, sir.

05:39.708 --> 05:41.166
You might get credit there.

05:45.250 --> 05:46.375
Lord Doyle!

05:50.958 --> 05:52.958
Oh. Mounts up, doesn't it?

05:53.666 --> 05:56.416
A prompt settlement
would be best for everyone, Lord Doyle.

05:56.500 --> 05:58.041
Of course. Of course.

05:58.125 --> 05:59.541
I shall call my banker in London

05:59.625 --> 06:01.791
and have him wire you
the outstanding amount immediately.

06:01.875 --> 06:03.416
-Lord Doyle!
-It is a Saturday.

06:03.916 --> 06:08.333
Banks are closed in the UK.
Sunday tomorrow, bank holiday Monday.

06:08.416 --> 06:11.208
My account manager will be back at work
first thing Tuesday morning.

06:11.708 --> 06:14.375
Tuesday afternoon, our time.
Will that suit?

06:14.458 --> 06:18.250
The full balance of HK$352,000.64

06:18.333 --> 06:22.333
must be paid by noon
on Tuesday, Lord Doyle,

06:22.416 --> 06:25.833
or I'll be forced to notify the police.

06:27.416 --> 06:28.625
Noon on Tuesday.

06:30.791 --> 06:32.000
You have three days.

07:07.916 --> 07:10.125
In Macau, I am a gwai lo,

07:12.625 --> 07:13.791
a foreign ghost…

07:15.583 --> 07:17.708
cloaked in invisibility.

07:27.041 --> 07:28.916
Here, I barely exist.

07:34.750 --> 07:37.958
Here, I can be whoever I want to be.

08:01.750 --> 08:05.083
Punto banco baccarat
is the fastest card game on the planet.

08:06.208 --> 08:09.083
Millions can be won or lost
in a single bet.

08:09.833 --> 08:12.666
And with a mere .9 advantage
to the casino,

08:13.166 --> 08:17.291
the prince of card games
can change your life in an instant.

08:39.291 --> 08:40.666
The rules are simple.

08:42.458 --> 08:46.041
Two cards are dealt face down
to the player with the highest wager.

08:46.541 --> 08:48.833
Highest hand wins.

08:49.500 --> 08:51.791
Cards two to nine score face value.

08:53.125 --> 08:55.958
Tens and picture cards score nothing.

08:59.666 --> 09:02.041
Highest score is nine.

09:04.250 --> 09:05.250
Nine wins!

09:06.000 --> 09:06.833
Player takes all.

09:14.083 --> 09:17.041
Welcome to the Rainbow. May I interest you
in a glass of champagne, sir?

09:17.125 --> 09:19.041
I don't want any cheap champagne.

09:19.125 --> 09:21.125
-Just give me Cristal.
-Okay.

09:22.666 --> 09:24.208
You speak good Chinese.

09:24.708 --> 09:27.916
I smoke Chinese cigarettes too.
The kind that kill.

09:30.500 --> 09:31.708
My name is Dao Ming.

09:32.208 --> 09:34.166
Really? Lord Doyle.

09:34.666 --> 09:36.750
An honor to meet you, Lord Doyle.

09:37.500 --> 09:39.416
Have you played baccarat before?

09:39.500 --> 09:42.500
Once or twice. Mostly in Monte Carlo.

09:44.041 --> 09:45.458
Who's the old biddy?

09:46.166 --> 09:47.916
-That's Grandma.
-Grandma?

09:48.000 --> 09:50.375
We don't speak her name. She's a killer.

09:50.458 --> 09:53.041
Her husband fools around
while she spends his money.

09:53.125 --> 09:55.541
-It's a good arrangement for us.
-Killer, is she?

09:55.625 --> 09:57.166
They say she sees spirits.

09:57.666 --> 10:00.250
Well, let's hope they don't tell her
what's on the cards.

10:19.541 --> 10:20.666
Nine wins.

10:22.500 --> 10:24.750
Death by guillotine. That's why I love it.

10:24.833 --> 10:26.958
Nothing like it in the universe.

10:27.041 --> 10:30.208
-The gwai lo is screwing up badly.
-He has the look of bad luck.

10:30.291 --> 10:32.916
My Cantonese is rusty. What did she say?

10:33.000 --> 10:34.000
Grandma welcomes you.

10:34.083 --> 10:37.291
I can burst his balls with one hand.

10:37.375 --> 10:39.333
Surely a lord has deep pockets.

10:39.416 --> 10:40.875
Only millionaires play in gloves.

10:40.958 --> 10:44.791
You'll need billions to beat Grandma.
Billions of dollars and no sense.

10:45.291 --> 10:48.291
-Her luck will run out.
-Not if the spirit world is with her.

10:48.375 --> 10:49.375
Spirit world, my arse.

10:49.458 --> 10:52.833
The only thing on Grandma's side
is her husband's wallet. Twenty thousand.

10:52.916 --> 10:54.708
-Thirty.
-Thirty-five.

10:55.583 --> 10:56.750
Fifty.

11:45.250 --> 11:47.208
-Hey. Do you want credit?
-Credit?

11:47.708 --> 11:50.791
Twenty thousand US at 15% plus commission.

11:51.375 --> 11:53.083
Fifty thousand at ten.

11:53.166 --> 11:54.666
Twenty-five at 12.

11:55.375 --> 11:56.250
Done.

11:56.333 --> 11:58.791
What the fuck? You gonna lend him money?

11:59.291 --> 12:01.458
Just look at his dick face.
His luck has run out.

12:01.541 --> 12:04.458
-What did she say?
-She says you're a bad gambler.

12:04.958 --> 12:08.500
Well, then, all the more reason
to open me that line of credit.

12:08.583 --> 12:10.250
Fuck credit! You're a loan shark.

12:10.333 --> 12:13.083
-This transaction will fucking kill you!
-Let me worry about that.

12:13.166 --> 12:15.166
-Is there a problem?
-No.

12:16.750 --> 12:20.541
Your bar bill. Settle up first,
and we'll take care of your credit line.

12:20.625 --> 12:21.875
Of… course.

12:21.958 --> 12:23.541
He's gonna make an escape.

12:24.041 --> 12:26.541
Actually, why don't you order
another bottle of bubbly,

12:26.625 --> 12:30.041
and I'll come back from the men's room
and skin her alive?

12:32.041 --> 12:33.125
Wait here?

12:36.958 --> 12:37.958
Of course.

12:38.875 --> 12:39.875
Thank you.

12:43.583 --> 12:45.416
Don't fucking do it.

12:45.500 --> 12:47.708
The bastard won't come back.

12:47.791 --> 12:49.041
You stupid cunt.

12:49.875 --> 12:51.708
He's a lost soul.

12:59.875 --> 13:01.041
Oh fuck.

13:05.458 --> 13:08.125
Today marks the first day

13:08.208 --> 13:11.791
