13:11.875 --> 13:16.583
Residents from all over the city
bring offerings to be burned for the dead,

13:16.666 --> 13:19.333
honoring and appeasing restless spirits.

13:52.208 --> 13:53.208
Thank you.

14:47.583 --> 14:49.958
Why did you lend him the money?

14:50.041 --> 14:51.791
-Dao Ming.
-I am sorry.

14:51.875 --> 14:54.625
-My husband died because of you!
-Hey! Hey, hey!

14:54.708 --> 14:56.041
Hey, hey, hey! Whoa, whoa!

14:58.875 --> 15:01.583
-I want my husband back!
-Dao Ming!

15:02.083 --> 15:04.541
-You killed my husband!
-Dao Ming!

15:11.708 --> 15:13.541
Taxi! Taxi!

15:21.541 --> 15:22.458
Dao Ming!

15:38.958 --> 15:40.125
Where are you going?

15:41.541 --> 15:43.875
You owe me 300 US for the champagne.

15:43.958 --> 15:45.583
