15:52.291 --> 15:53.291
Thank you.

16:06.708 --> 16:07.541
Wait!

16:08.208 --> 16:09.791
I'd like to make it up to you.

16:10.833 --> 16:11.666
How about…

16:11.750 --> 16:13.583
How about dinner and a dance?

16:13.666 --> 16:15.833
You know, we could come
to some arrangement.

16:15.916 --> 16:17.500
I hate gamblers.

16:17.583 --> 16:20.250
I'm standing at a statistical crossroads.

16:20.333 --> 16:21.583
It's possible I keep on losing,

16:21.666 --> 16:24.208
but probability says
I have to start winning.

16:24.291 --> 16:25.958
Probability won't save you.

16:26.041 --> 16:29.666
Well, isn't that what life is?
The statistical improbability.

16:29.750 --> 16:31.625
Life is a mysterious gift.

16:32.125 --> 16:34.833
Look, I… I played my way into this mess.

16:34.916 --> 16:37.375
With the right backing,
I can play my way out.

16:41.125 --> 16:42.375
Look, look, look.

16:43.208 --> 16:44.458
I've had a run of bad luck.

16:44.958 --> 16:46.958
I've tried all the usual creditors, but…

16:48.125 --> 16:49.416
