-What, money?

29:04.875 --> 29:06.458
-Justice.
-Justice?

29:07.375 --> 29:08.250
All right.

29:09.458 --> 29:12.375
You lend me $500, you can have
all the fucking justice you want.

29:12.458 --> 29:14.208
Lord Doyle, you're such a card.

29:14.291 --> 29:16.375
You want my photo?
I'm just giving you terms.

29:16.458 --> 29:17.916
-Terms?
-Yeah, terms. Why not?

29:18.000 --> 29:19.958
