another crack at me with your camera

29:30.083 --> 29:31.541
so you can email my photo back

29:31.625 --> 29:35.083
to whatever tawdry little
private investigator's firm sent you here

29:35.166 --> 29:37.166
to do whatever the fuck
you came here to do,

29:37.250 --> 29:38.875
which is probably to threaten me.

29:40.916 --> 29:43.541
