not unless you damn well pay me.

29:46.333 --> 29:49.458
So come on, Betty,
get off your high horse. Fork it over.

29:49.541 --> 29:51.500
I want 500 US now.

29:53.041 --> 29:54.875
Down to your last penny, are you,

29:55.583 --> 29:56.916
Mr. Reilly?

30:03.041 --> 30:04.041
Hey!

30:06.166 --> 30:07.416
Excuse… Excuse me.

30:11.666 --> 30:13.083
-Fuck!
-Reilly!

31:27.083 --> 31:29.875
I've beaten better men than you
at this game.

31:31.000 --> 31:32.375
Give me my handbag.

31:38.291 --> 31:41.333
-Where the bloody hell's my phone?
-I want the 500 first.

31:42.166 --> 31:44.875
-Give me the phone.
-Money first, then photo.

31:53.583 --> 31:54.583
Thank you.

31:55.583 --> 31:57.250
What about my phone?

32:01.833 --> 32:03.416
We had an agreement.

32:04.000 --> 32:05.666
My photo's worth more than 500.

32:05.750 --> 32:07.291
Your only hope is to sit back, relax,

32:07.375 --> 32:09.625
and marvel
while I turn this into ten grand.

32:10.500 --> 32:12.500
Watch and learn, Betty.

32:34.833 --> 32:36.333
This is to leave me alone.

32:36.416 --> 32:38.041
No, we made a deal.

32:38.583 --> 32:41.541
Look, I'm offering you the equivalent
of 10,000 US dollars. Just take it.

32:41.625 --> 32:42.750
I can't.

32:42.833 --> 32:44.166
Of course you can.

32:44.666 --> 32:46.250
You can't afford not to. This is…

32:46.750 --> 32:49.625
Ten thousand is the conservatory
you always wanted. A Caribbean holiday.

32:49.708 --> 32:51.666
New kitchen. Decent clothes.

32:53.166 --> 32:55.583
You never were gonna
give me back my phone, were you?

32:56.083 --> 32:57.375
Isn't this much better?

32:58.708 --> 33:01.375
Not everybody is like you.

33:06.833 --> 33:07.666
Wait!

33:07.750 --> 33:09.333
For fuck's sake.

33:10.000 --> 33:13.500
Wait. Look, look, I've made some mistakes
in the past, right?

33:13.583 --> 33:17.958
Who hasn't? But the point is, look,
I… I'm trying to make a new start. Right?

33:18.041 --> 33:21.250
Now, whatever you might think of me,
I'm not a criminal.

33:22.250 --> 33:25.333
You stole a considerable sum
of money from our client.

33:26.500 --> 33:30.125
And the fact that you quite evidently have
a gambling problem is not an excuse--

33:30.208 --> 33:32.375
I do not have a gambling problem.

33:32.875 --> 33:33.791
Okay? Now…

33:34.541 --> 33:37.000
Look, how about…
how about dinner and a dance?

33:37.083 --> 33:39.666
You know? I mean,
maybe we can come to some arrangement.

33:39.750 --> 33:41.416
I beg your pardon?

33:41.500 --> 33:43.666
I'm asking you to dance, Betty.

33:43.750 --> 33:45.291
How dare you!

33:45.375 --> 33:47.875
-Live a little!
-Oh, bugger off!

33:49.416 --> 33:51.666
Well, at least take the 500 I owe you.

33:52.250 --> 33:56.500
Keep it. You'll only blow it all
on the next round of baccarat.

33:57.333 --> 33:59.250
Bloody gamblers!

34:04.250 --> 34:05.083
Fuck.

34:13.708 --> 34:15.458
You're running out of puff.

34:15.958 --> 34:19.833
I may be out of puff,
but… I still have my balls.

34:21.041 --> 34:23.333
Yeah, right. Not for long.

34:42.208 --> 34:43.958
Grandma scores another nine.

34:45.000 --> 34:47.041
Not so lucky after all, huh?

34:50.958 --> 34:52.333
Well, I… I should…

34:54.250 --> 34:55.416
